provisions.content:
(a)     state the names of the members of the inspection team by whom the inspection
is to be carried out;
(b)     contain the name of the person in charge of the in-country escorts;
(c)     in the case of a challenge inspection, also state the name of any observer who
may accompany the team;
(d)     contain a description of the specified area in which the inspection is to be
conducted; and
(e)     specify the type of inspection concerned.
